---
---

<section class="max-w-[1200px] mx-auto px-margin-mobile md:px-margin-desktop py-20">
  <h2 class="font-fredoka text-display-lg-mobile md:text-headline-lg text-primary text-center mb-xl">
    Kenapa Membangun Karakter itu Penting?
  </h2>
  <div class="grid grid-cols-12 gap-6">
    <!-- Large Card: Filosofi Berbasis Riset -->
    <div
      class="col-span-12 md:col-span-8 bg-white p-xl rounded-3xl shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow scroll-reveal"
    >
      <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-lg">
        <div class="md:w-1/2 flex flex-col justify-center order-2 md:order-1">
          <span class="text-primary font-bold text-body-lg uppercase tracking-wider mb-sm font-fredoka"
            >Berbasis Riset</span
          >
          <h4 class="font-fredoka text-headline-lg mb-md">
            Soft Skill Memprediksi Kesuksesan Hidup
          </h4>
          <p class="text-secondary font-body-lg mb-md">
            Pemenang Nobel Ekonomi James Heckman membuktikan: soft skill seperti
            jujur, disiplin, dan mandiri memprediksi kesuksesan hidup setara atau
            lebih kuat dari IQ. Investasi di masa kecil memberikan ROI 7–10% per tahun.
          </p>
          <ul class="space-y-sm">
            <li class="flex items-center gap-sm text-on-surface-variant text-body-lg">
              <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary"
                >check_circle</span
              >
              <span>Jujur, Disiplin, Mandiri — fondasi karakter</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-sm text-on-surface-variant text-body-lg">
              <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary"
                >check_circle</span
              >
              <span>Investasi early childhood: ROI 7–10%/tahun (Heckman, 2012)</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="md:w-1/2 order-1 md:order-2">
          <img
            class="w-full h-full object-cover rounded-2xl"
            alt="Lingkungan belajar alami"
            src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuBSSm386qF6d9_Zm87Xu3ylCnZIO5T5CnGd_1HMVaNWNf-vBc8PSRQ9OUfkaSTsK5KdkQlE3gdnsEzsqmSSh2TOyHmIQtGs7VN5gdsHu3kfh_v9zff_3FyPYI4wOtn3w1PWL6zS137Vzn3-zcPW_jIUqsi9XU0QTseDkzwQ1_m13db_K48nEAU7WVOB0qY_ugqp3troHrmUNVHTrZxHeitgxv7rGG82rKWgBoxATCcrdEsVZIfWyq1TM9lBnDSYxqGQiUGnb3t9WBoZ"
          />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <!-- Stats Card -->
    <div
      class="col-span-12 md:col-span-4 bg-primary-container text-on-primary-container p-xl rounded-3xl shadow-sm flex flex-col justify-between scroll-reveal"
    >
      <div>
        <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-5xl mb-md font-fredoka"
          >analytics</span
        >
        <h4 class="font-fredoka text-headline-lg mb-sm">Tracking Karakter</h4>
        <p class="font-fredoka text-body-lg opacity-90">
          Pantau perkembangan karakter anak secara real-time. Lihat bagaimana
          setiap sesi bermain membentuk kepribadian yang lebih baik.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="mt-lg pt-lg border-t border-on-primary-container/20">
        <div class="text-5xl font-bold font-fredoka">7–10%</div>
        <div class="text-body-lg">ROI per tahun dari investasi early childhood (Heckman Equation)</div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <!-- Screen Time -->
    <div
      class="col-span-12 md:col-span-4 bg-secondary-container p-xl rounded-3xl shadow-sm scroll-reveal"
    >
      <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-5xl mb-md"
        >phone_iphone</span
      >
      <h4 class="font-fredoka text-headline-lg mb-sm">Screen Time Merusak</h4>
      <p class="text-secondary font-body-lg">
        Jonathan Haidt (NYU, 2024) membuktikan: screen-based childhood merusak
        perkembangan sosial-emosional anak. Offline play adalah solusinya.
      </p>
    </div>
    <!-- Sekolah Belum Optimal -->
    <div
      class="col-span-12 md:col-span-4 bg-tertiary-container/20 p-xl rounded-3xl shadow-sm scroll-reveal"
    >
      <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-tertiary text-5xl mb-md"
        >school</span
      >
      <h4 class="font-fredoka text-headline-lg mb-sm">Sekolah Belum Optimal</h4>
      <p class="text-secondary font-body-lg">
        Riset Indonesia 2024–2026 menunjukkan: implementasi soft skill di sekolah
        masih terhambat waktu, metode, dan evaluasi. Kepompong hadir untuk melengkapi.
      </p>
    </div>
    <!-- Aktivitas Terstruktur -->
    <div
      class="col-span-12 md:col-span-4 bg-surface p-xl rounded-3xl shadow-sm border border-outline-variant scroll-reveal"
    >
      <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-5xl mb-md"
        >event_available</span
      >
      <h4 class="font-fredoka text-headline-lg mb-sm">Aktivitas Terstruktur</h4>
      <p class="text-secondary font-body-lg">
        Meta-analisis 17 studi: aktivitas terstruktur meningkatkan social skills
        anak dengan effect size 0.862. Kepompong menyediakannya instan, 3 detik.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
